query:
SELECT 
                    id,
                    event_class,
                    display_name,
                    occurred_at,
                    severity,
                    attributes,
                    user_id
                FROM monitoring_events_timeline
                WHERE occurred_at >= $1
                  AND event_class = ANY($2)
                  AND ($3::text IS NULL OR severity = $3)
                ORDER BY occurred_at DESC
                LIMIT $4 OFFSET $5
